---
title: Cheesy Chorizo and Beef Burger with salad and sweet potato fries
description: The juicy cheeseburger contains both beef and chorizo, for a meal that's mighty meaty. A paprika aioli and sweet potato fries accompany, along with a fresh side salad for a hint of health.
